text: Celestino Vercelli (10 August 1946 - 26 November 2020) was an Italian professional racing cyclist. He rode in the 1971 and 1976 Tour de France. Vercelli died on 26 November 2020 at the age of 74. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Tour de France cyclists Category:Italian cyclists
